# Change Documentation

After a substantial change is complete, add one markdown file in `.agents/docs/`.

- Filename: kebab-case, e.g. `checkout-flow.md` or `payment-handler.md`

## Template

```markdown
# Change title

## Summary
What was added or changed.

## Code areas
- Layers / paths touched: …
- Main files: …

## Verification
1. {{devCommand}}
2. Manual steps: …
```
